A three-year-old   child from Diepkloof, Soweto, was allegedly repeatedly beaten and raped by her teen mother's boyfriend before   she succumbed to her injuries last week. The mother, 17, who is heavily pregnant, and her boyfriend are said to be on the run after the death of the  child at Chris Hani Baragwanath Academic Hospital in Soweto on Thursday night. Bara spokesperson Nkosiyethu Mazibuko said the child  was admitted on Monday last week for suspected sexual assault in view of genital and anal lacerations. For more on this story, please visit SowetanLIVE.